about 7-10 minutes, and the price is about 12 PLN. Other non-corporate taxi
services are not recommended! If you arrive at ?=F3d? Kaliska Railway
Station, located in the south-western part of the city, the best connection
to the venue of the conference is by taxi. The same two corporations are
